  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add onion, garlic, and ginger. Cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add chicken. Cook until browned on all sides.",
    "Add curry powder, cumin, coriander, salt, and pepper. Cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add coconut milk and water. Stir to combine.",
    "Bring to a simmer. Reduce heat to low. Cover and cook for 20-25 minutes or until the chicken is cooked through.",
